text: Shakhovskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Pavlovsky District of Ulyanovsk Oblast, Russia.Law #126-ZO ==Notable people== Soviet statesman Mikhail Suslov was born here in 1902. ==References== ===Notes=== ===Sources=== * * Category:Rural localities in Ulyanovsk Oblast __NOTOC__
title: Shakhovskoye, Ulyanovsk Oblast
